{"tid":1947282,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"耿爽指出個別國家在聯合國框架外實施單邊制裁，無異於雪上加霜、落井下石","createTime":"2020-03-28T07:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T11:13:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"28807b8ae2c383436defa2e08ea2b3b1edf7ec69","tid":1947282,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"二十國集團昨日召開特別峰會，討論武漢肺炎的應對措施。在北京，外交部支持聯合國秘書長古特雷斯呼籲，解除可能破壞各國應對疫情的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n發言人耿爽不點名批評美國，指出個別國家在聯合國框架外實施單邊制裁，當前疫情正在全球擴散蔓延，國際社會積極開展抗疫合作是當務之急，如果持續施加單邊制裁，無異於雪上加霜、落井下石，嚴重影響聯合國及其他國際組織開展人道主義援助。<br />\n<br />\n另外，外交部批評美國《華爾街日報》上月刊登的評論，指出中方不接受信中透出的傲慢與偏見，中方不歡迎不客觀、不公正的報道，形容《華爾街日報》欠中國人民一個道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1517280_1_20200327191504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1517280_1_20200327191504.jpg&h=0acf5f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517280-20200327.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517280-20200327.htm&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=09ea28bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517280-20200327.htm&h=ceb2b1dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517280-20200327.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n佢真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f3144912b3a406e6bd743e6b8700e30ccc269b","tid":1947282,"uid":9542,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"美國當初咪撚比隻藥呢啲臭閪國家，正宗解釋到咩叫人心當狗肺，仲比人反咬幾啖"},{"pid":"4afe9e76de9ec967184c69a14e022036eaf3a010","tid":1947282,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s